      "type": "concept_card",
      "title": "The Division Equation",
      "content": "When you know the total and number of groups, write: Total ÷ Groups = Each. Example: 28 total ÷ 7 groups = 4 each. The answer (quotient) tells you the size of each group. Check: 7 × 4 = 28. ✓",
